rows.label: campfev11_080_100_msg0002
rows.name: This can only be the work of an Grail...

rows.label: campfev11_080_100_msg0004
rows.name:
I hope we'll be able to meet up
with Kasumi. I'm starting to get a little
worried.

rows.label: campfev11_080_100_msg0006
rows.name:
We've no option but to trust in
the plan.

rows.label: campfev11_080_100_msg0008
rows.name:
But first, we've got a more urgent
matter to attend to...

rows.label: campfev11_080_100_msg0009
rows.name:
Indeed. When we've taken care of
it, let's wait for Kasumi at Felt.
